Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Kenta Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm just a regular guy, an average student.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since l met Suwatee, Shuree and the Gods of Luck, my life has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been getting as much action as l can handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Life is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this gorgeous nurse, Haruna Sakamoto, appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to share all the happiness of life with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! l've never been this happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Can Bunny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Can Bunny\NExtra 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:54.80,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiryuka Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she didn't come home last night. Mr. Okamura is very worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll help look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were the last people to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably out playing somewhere.\NAfter all, she is a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Shuree?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.26,0:01:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l think it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cross that Haruna wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her grandfather Sakamoto and l were best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left this cross to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel strong spiritual energy coming from the cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the same presence l felt yesterday in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that cross have some kind of story behind it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cross belonged to my old lover, Kyoko Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years ago, this was an army hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto and l worked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no hope for the future then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We nursed people while waiting for our own deaths at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she appeared in front of us... Kyoko Kawashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was working in the same hospital as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l fell in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko and l made a promise that after the war, we would be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But while l was visiting my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto took the cross from her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt was then l finally realized he also loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war finally ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto found a woman who looked like Kyoko and married her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna strongly resembles Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things that remain are the flower garden and fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake. lt's the same spiritual signature as the cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Haruna was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, forgive me! Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spiritual energy is getting stronger! Kenta, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will, but where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Haruna is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help me! Uncle, help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, stop it! Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l must go! Haruna! Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna's in there. l'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O spirits of the air around me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits that rule time and space, in the name of Kishoten, l command thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine your powers with mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, it's coming from where the old man is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, you can't! Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, forgive me! Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! l'll call a nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm fine. Take me to the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko is the one who kidnapped Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's her anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:04:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l went to visit my family, Kyoko was already pregnant with my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l was forced into an arranged marriage by my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't tell Kyoko what had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l didn't return, she forced Sakamoto to tell her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night Kyoko was going to come after me, she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she had every right to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then l've dedicated my life to this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l beg you, Kenta! Please take me to the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, you're there, aren't you? lt's me! Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, please let that child go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi, l've been so lonely and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l believed that you would come back, so l've been waiting all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you coming back to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Haruna has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the one who betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's too late to ask you to forgive me, but that child is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't let my child go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. That child is Sakamoto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l'm taking us back to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years ago, Kyoko died here full of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take the old man back and have him meet the living Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way if you want to save those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of present, past, future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln the name of the Kishoten, l command thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of the air around me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my hand and set free the substance of space!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relive the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is fifty years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko! Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Kyoko! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi, is it you? My eyes! l can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come back. Sakamoto said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby... l didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wanted to see you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's hard to breathe. Dearest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me. Stay by my side always, please. The three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko, wait! l still have things that l need to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right. lt's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Okamura is safely back in his hospital room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mysterious woman is really powerful, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay. l won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now l understand why Grandfather cherished that cross so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why Uncle Okamura treasures me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko was wonderful, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful and kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was so scared! So very scared, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! What am l doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've never felt these feelings before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l really like you, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why doesn't he just go for it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l've never...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you don't want to, Haruna, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, l want to be with you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'll be all right. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, you're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, relax your thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, hurry. l can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Haruna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta's being extra gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's really fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, you're very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm embarrassed, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think l'm disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it okay, Haruna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my chest hurt? Kenta, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's so delicate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.45,0:12:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm afraid l'll break her if l move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna, l can't hold back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay, Kenta, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't l stop crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry. Did l hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l made you happy, then l'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lousy day! lt's pouring down rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, have you seen Shuree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lsn't she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought she was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l haven't seen her since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that l think of it, you really are quite beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That stupid guy has me all confused.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, why do you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you confess your love to Kenta, tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, l'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, what would you do if l weren't here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would l do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have a crush on me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if l do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l did, would that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if l liked you, we couldn't do anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you tell Kenta how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Do you plan to marry that old man without even touching the one you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if l touch him with the power of the star, the memory will be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l could be with Kenta, love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd rather die with all those memories than live without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you don't do something, then l'll take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's someone l wasn't supposed to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't turn on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta! You insensitive bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope things go well with all the girls you laid! Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:40.61,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Here Come the Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lonely when we don't see you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l'm sorry. This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l really loved you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are others who love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll be okay without me, right? So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon you'll marry the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to? But now it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, save me! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want to leave Kenta after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay if l can't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to be by his side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you a spoiled princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it really enough just to be by his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then give the piece of the star to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the one who stole the piece of star. l was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll get married for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No way! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, it won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Be quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way you can be by Kenta's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, be good to Kenta, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kishoten, huh? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor Shibi, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l am the one who stole the piece of star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, l'm saying l'll be your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or don't you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though your beauty has a different flavor from Suwatee's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can l ask you one favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt would be hard to say no to a beauty like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shuree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Did you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, l forgot to say something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if l told you that l liked you, Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that were true, we couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Suwatee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O spirit of the star, mirror my form!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide what can be seen, show what is hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can touch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, your hands are faster than your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, what's happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l... l didn't know what else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, don't you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay. l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.19,0:21:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was so mean to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you said that l was pretty, it made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l meant it. You really are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's okay even if you don't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, are you teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me. l really love you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suwatee, it's your own fault, because you waited too long!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, look at the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm embarrassed after all, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, l do like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, let me love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shuree, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, that's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l can't wait any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, you look so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After this. After this, l can forget him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! More! Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:23:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta! More! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, l'm coming. You, come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.68,0:24:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.42,0:24:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, you were wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.56,0:24:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.33,0:24:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.47,0:24:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.97,0:24:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Don't forget about me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.98,0:24:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't forget me. Don't forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.41,0:25:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that all you're going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:19.23,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl: ''No! After this, please no more!''\NMakoto: ''Hehehe! Don't move around so much!''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.37,0:25:20.80,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl: ''l love you! l'm never letting you go!''\NMakoto: ''Wait a minute!''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.60,0:25:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess there's such a thing as too much love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.14,0:25:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.22,0:25:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been a while, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.12,0:25:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Suwatee!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.79,0:25:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, this time you do remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.82,0:25:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwatee, why are you hanging out with this loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.49,0:25:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree, you came back too?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.40,0:25:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shuree, what do you mean by loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.40,0:25:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure friendly. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.84,0:25:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.60,0:25:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.14,0:25:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.31,0:26:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.41,0:26:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.78,0:26:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when was ''that time?''
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.14,0:26:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time when you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.51,0:26:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Why would l come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.48,0:26:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ldiot! l can't talk about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.48,0:26:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, say it, you creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.42,0:26:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.62,0:26:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.66,0:26:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you used the\Nstar's power with Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.99,0:26:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.46,0:26:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfair! You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.93,0:26:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you ignored me, but you did it with Shuree!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.70,0:26:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.44,0:26:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Suwatee is getting upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.34,0:26:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's headed for a love triangle with Shuree!
